    <abstract>
      <t>This document describes an XML-based protocol for mapping service identifiers and geodetic or civic location information to service contact URIs.  In particular, it can be used to determine the location-appropriate Public Safety Answering Point (PSAP) for emergency services. [STANDARDS-TRACK]
	 </t>
